ation%2C%20we%20decide%20not%20to%20go%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ad06694-e764-4b62-b50d-d858f1af71fe%5C%22%3EKlarna%20gears%20up%20for%20US%20IPO%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202005%2C%20Klarna%20offers%20short-term%20financing%20to%20customers%20online%20and%20in-store%20at%20checkout.%20It%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%20600%2C00%20merchants%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20Adidas%2C%20and%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20has%20been%20a%20mainstay%20for%20Klarna%2C%20which%20in%202021%20was%20valued%20at%20%2445.6%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20the%20most%20valuable%20startup%20in%20Europe%20at%20the%20time.%20Its%20valuation%20fell%20to%20%246.7%20billion%20in%202022%20during%20a%20wider%20market%20downturn%20for%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20banks%20to%20IPO%20in%20the%20US%2C%20at%20a%20%2420%20billion%20valuation%2C%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-27%2Fklarna-said-to-sound-out-banks-for-us-ipo-at-20-billion-value%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20Klarna%20has%20ramped%20up%20its%20activity%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20a%20partnership%20with%20Uber%20and%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20cashback%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Klarna%20said%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klarna.com%2Finternational%2Fregulatory-news%2Fklarna-h1-earnings-compounding-growth-generates-27-revenue-rise-sek-11-billion-profit-improvement-and-over-sek-1-trillion-annualized-gmv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20gross%20profits%3C%2Fa%3E%20increased%20by%2093%25%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%20on%20a%20year-over-year%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Klarna%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20Jyoti%20Mann%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3Ejyotimann.11%3C