n%20outside%20the%20traditional%20TV%20spot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-amazon-branded-entertainment-playbook-amy-powell-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Pak%20Match%20Soon%3F%20Cricket%20Comes%20Up%20In%20S%20Jaishankar's%20Islamabad%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECricket%20featured%20as%20a%20talking%20point%20between%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20his%20Pakistani%20counterpart%20Ishaq%20Dar%20during%20an%20official%20lunch%20hosted%20by%20Pakistani%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20and%20Mr%20Dar%2C%20who%20sat%20next%20to%20each%20other%20during%20the%20lunch%2C%20held%20only%20informal%20talks%20over%20cricket%20and%20there%20was%20no%20formal%20discussion%20over%20resumption%20of%20cricketing%20ties%2C%20sources%20added.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20direct%20conversation%20since%202015%20between%20the%20two%20countries'%20foreign%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20chief%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20dinner%20meet%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20content%20of%20the%20talks%20is%20not%20known%2C%20sources%20said%20that%20Pakistan%20wants%20India%20to%20send%20its%20team%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20set%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20the%20neighbouring%20nation%20next%20February.%20Top%20officials%20of%20the%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20had%20recently%20told%20the%20PCB%20that%20organising%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20without%20India%20will%20be%20meaningless%20since%20it%20will%20impact%20the%20ICC's%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20not%20played%20any%20match%20in%20Pakistan%20since%20the%202008%20Asia%20Cup%20due%20to%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20arisin