p%3EHowever%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20rules%20in%20the%20case%20of%20some%20day-time%20express%20trains%2C%20where%20a%20shorter%20time%20limit%20for%20advance%20reservation%20is%20currently%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20also%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20365-day%20time%20period%20for%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20around%2030-35%20crore%20passengers%20travel%20on%20Indian%20trains%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729157760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F7h30t15o_train-generic_625x300_30_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-railways-changes-rules-for-advance-ticket-booking-reduces-it-from-120-days-to-6809760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Passengers%20earlier%20were%20able%20to%20book%20train%20tickets%20120%20days%20in%20advance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-railways-changes-rules-for-advance-ticket-booking-reduces-it-from-120-days-to-6809760%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Think%20Micro%2C%20Act%20Inclusive%3A%20How%20Haryana%20Is%20Shaping%20BJP%20Maharashtra%20Campaign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBJP's%20historic%20win%20in%20Haryana%20has%20prompted%20the%20party%20to%20approach%20Maharashtra%20elections%20with%20a%20far%20more%20confident%20strategy%20mainly%20centred%20around%20five%20important%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20all%20set%20to%20fight%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20around%20155%2C%20and%20wants%20to%20ensure%20it%20projects%20a%20unified%20campaign%20with%20its%20allies%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20while%20maximising%20the%20optimism%20among%20voters%20surrounding%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojana%20announced%20by%20the%20ruling%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReaching%20out%20to%20non-dominant%20communities%20and%20reducing%20the%20impact%20of%20Maratha%20agitation%20demands%2C%20ensuring%20vote%20transfer%20among%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20running%20a%20campaign%20that%20addresses%20social%20and%20political%20anti-incumbency%20at%20the%20micro%20level%20are%20also%20top%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20central%20election%20committee%20of%20the%20party%20met%20at%20the%20party%20headquarters%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20too%20was%20present%2C%20along%20with%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%2C%20sources%20said%20BJP%20could%20come%20out%20with%20its%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20within%20two%20days%20and%20could%20fight%20on%20154%20to%20158%20seats%20in%20the%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20with%20105%20seats%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%20of%20the%20state.%20Its%20then%20ally%20-%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20had%20won%2056%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20undivided%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Congress-led%20UPA%2C%20had%20won%2041%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20had%20won%2044%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20now%20eyeing%20a%20comeback%20after%20a%20dismal%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20six%20months%20ago%20where%20the%20party%20faced%20a%20setback%20winning%20only%209%20out%20of%2028%20contested%20seats.%20Maharashtra%20is%20particularly%20important%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20considering%20it%20houses%20the%20nation's%20commercial%20capital%20Mumbai%2C%20critical%20for%20investments%2C%20FDI%20and%20development%20focus%20of%20Modi%203.0%2C%20and%20also%20for%20issues%20of%20identity%2C%20including%20Maratha%20pride%20and%20prevalence%20of%20vocal%20Dalit-Ambekarite%20groups%20that%20have%20been%20critical%20opponents%20of%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatching%20Rivals%20Closely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20the%20BJP%20working%20on%20the%20campaign%20say%20the%20party%20will%20push%20the%20%26quot%3Bcognitive%20dissonance%26quot%3B%20in%20many%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20voters%20that%20they%20claim%20are%20upset%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20wherein%20the%20Congress%20won%2016%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20core%20Shiv%20Sena%20voter%20has%20never%20liked%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20while%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20vote%20transfer%20happened%20to%20its%20allies%2C%20the%20opposite%20didn't%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Congress%20did%20very%20well%2C%20even%20better%20than%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20that%20fought%20on%20difficult%20seats.%20This%20will%20work%20to%20our%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20is%20portrayed%20as%20the%20true%20Shiv%20Sainik%2C%20walking%20the%20path%20envisioned%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20founder%20Bal%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20even%20taking%20it%20further%20by%20connecting%20with%20the%20common%20man.%20As%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20has%20opened%20the%20doors%20of%20his%20official%20residence%2C%20Varsha%2C%20to%20the%20general%20public%20in%20a%20way%20no%20other%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20done%20before%2C%20making%20him%20relatable%20as%20a%20next-door%20Shiv%20Sainik.%20A%20party%20leader%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20cannot%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20barometer%20for%20what%20lies%20ahead%2C%20citing%20examples%20where%20the%20BJP%20won%205%20out%20of%206%20Assembly%20Constituency%20(AC)%20seats%20but%20lost%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20particularly%20in%20constituencies%20like%20Dhule%20and%20Malegaon.%20BJP%20insiders%20added%20that%20they%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20MVA's%20strategy%2C%20especially%20looking%20for%20any%20mistakes%20they%20may%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20announce%20Uddhav%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20we%20will%20rework%20our%20campaign%20too..but%20as%20of%20now%20that%20doesn't%20look%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20party%20leader%20in%20Maharashtra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20On%20Organisational%20Strengths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20definitive%20change%20in%20the%20Haryana%20campaign%20of%20the%20BJP%20was%20the%20larger%20involvement%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20with%20state%20in-charge%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20stressing%20optimising%20the%20organisational%20strength%20of%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDharmendra%20Pradhan%20comes%20from%20ABVP%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20RSS.%20He%20gets%20along%20very%20well%20with%20the%20RSS%2C%20specifically%20with%20leaders%20such%20as%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale.%20Similarly%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20has%20his%20origins%20in%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Adhivakta%20Parishad%2C%20the%20lawyer's%20wing%20of%20the%20RSS.%20He%20knows%20the%20value%20RSS%20brings%20to%20BJP%20so%20he%20has%20made%20the%20campaign%20worker%20centric%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20functionary%20of%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20of%20potential%20rebels.%20Senior%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20who%20is%20also%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20state%2C%20along%20with%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20who%20is%20also%20the%20co-prabhari%20for%20the%20state%20election%2C%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20talking%20to%20people.%20%26quot%3BKeeping%20the%20morale%20of%20workers%20high%20is%20top%20on%20the%20agenda.%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20been%20holding%20meetings%20with%20workers%20in%20groups%20of%201%2C500%20to%202%2C000%20to%20understand%20their%20problems%20to%20motivate%20them%20to%20keep%20working%2C%20which%20is%20why%20a%20lot%20is%20not%20being%20talked%20about%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20face%20so%20that%20workers%20of%20other%20parties%20don't%20get%20demotivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWelfare%20Works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trump%20card%20of%20the%20coalition's%20campaign%20however%20remains%20the%20populist%20measures%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20announced%2C%20from%20the%20Mukhya%20Manti%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojana%20%C2%A0-%20a%20monthly%20allowance%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%202.5%20crore%20women%20in%20the%2018%20to%2065-year%20age%20group%20and%20Diwali%20bonus%20to%20BMC%20workers.%20The%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojana%20has%20particularly%20generated%20an%20overwhelming%20response%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20it%20will%20be%20a%20game-changer%2C%20as%20similar%20schemes%20were%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chattisgarh%20where%20the%20BJP%20won%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year.%20The%20BJP%20is%20putting%20a%20lot%20of%20extra%20effort%20in%20Marathwada%20where%20it%20is%20working%20harder%20to%20ensure%20the%20agitation%20by%20Maratha%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20doesn't%20impact%20its%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20complete%20loss%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region%2C%20where%20it%20failed%20to%20secure%20any%20of%20the%208%20seats%2C%20is%20attributed%20to%20Maratha%20unrest%20over%20reservation%20issues.%20The%20BJP%20also%20faces%20challenges%20in%20retaining%20its%20dominance%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20trumped%20it%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAddressing%20Concerns%20Over%20Vote%20Transfer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20with%20its%20allies%20has%20decided%20that%20it%20will%20mount%20one%20common%20campaign%20with%20a%20common%20tagline%20to%20show%20a%20united%20face.%20%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20in%20the%20natural%20course%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20being%20fielded%20in%20direct%20contests%20with%20Congress%20and%20in%20seats%20where%20the%20OBC%20communities%20are%20dominant.%20Wherever%20there%20are%20Marathas%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20is%20our%20best%20bet.%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20candidates%20have%20pockets%20of%20influence%20which%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20functionary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unified%20campaign%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20allies%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20centred%20around%20projects%20executed%20by%20the%20Centre%20and%20%C2%A0Mahayuti%20government%2C%20and%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20executing%20projects%20stalled%20by%20the%20MVA.%20Sources%20said%20as%20of%20now%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20get%20former%20MPs%20to%20contest%20elections%20but%20family%20members%20of%20some%20netas%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20have%20proved%20their%20mettle%20in%20the%20past%20are%20likely%20to%20figure%20in%20the%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20much%20emphasis%20on%20symbols%20as%20vote%20transfer%20was%20a%20concern%20in%202024.%20Every%20leader's%20campaign%20will%20prominently%20feature%20symbols%20of%20allies.%20Joint%20rallies%20are%20being%20discussed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20functionary%20cited%20above%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20rallies%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20likely%20to%20begin%20after%20Diwali%20for%20maximum%20impact.%20There%20will%20at%20least%20be%20one%20PM%20rally%20in%20each%20of%20the%20six%20divisions%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutreach%20To%20All%20Castes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20smaller%2C%20non-Maratha%20communities%20too.%20A%20rainbow%20coalition%20of%20communities%20is%20what%20the%20BJP%20is%20looking%20at%2C%20taking%20a%20cue%20from%20its%20strategy%20in%20Haryana.%20Around%20100%20such%20meetings%20led%20by%20party%20leaders%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMuch%20focus%20on%20the%20Dalit%20vote%20drifting%20away%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0Sources%20said%20while%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20is%20working%20on%20Buddhist%20Dalits%20who%20constitute%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Dalit%20population%2C%20the%20party%20is%20hopeful%20that%20with%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20Dalits%20will%20come%20back%20to%20the%20party%20fold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20those%20dealing%20with%20caste%20and%20community%20outreach%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20party%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20communities%20such%20as%20Mahar%2C%20Chanar%2C%20Matang%2C%20Valmiki%20and%20others.%20%26quot%3BExcept%20a%20few%2C%20many%20of%20them%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20at%20least%20some%20time.%20So%20we%20are%20working%20on%20them%20to%20get%20their%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20functionary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20OBC%20communities%20like%20Dhankhar%2C%20Mali%2C%20Kunbi%2C%20Vanjari%20and%20at%20least%2050%20others%20have%20been%20the%20BJP's%20core%20strength.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20have%20at%20least%2025%20Maratha%20leaders%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20that%20we%20will%20project%20prominently.%20The%20party%20has%20had%20over%2045%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Marathas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20nine%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20of%20which%20Nandurbar%2C%20Gadchiroli-Chimur%2C%20Palghar%20and%20Dindori%20are%20reserved%20for%20STs%2C%20while%20Amaravati%2C%20Ramtek%2C%20Latur%2C%20Solapur%20and%20Shirdi%20are%20reserved%20for%20SCs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20nine%20seats%2C%20Congress%20won%20six%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20BJP%20managed%20just%20one%2C%20down%20from%20its%20tally%20of%20seven%20in%202019.%20Minority%20Affairs%20minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20cabinet%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20has%20been%20specifically%20tasked%20with%20reaching%20out%20to%20neo-Buddhists%2C%20who%20comprise%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20Dalit%20population%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20rallying%20with%20the%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20party%20will%20cut%20into%20some%20Opposition%20votes%2C%20BJP%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20smaller%20parties%20have%20also%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20Maharashtra%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpotlight%20On%20Micro%20Issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20micro%20outlook%20that%20the%20BJP%20says%20will%20help%20it%20drive%20its%20results.%20There%20are%20identity%20issues%20such%20as%20Maratha%20reservation%20and%20split%20in%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20but%20there%20are%20identity%20issues%20such%20as%20inflation%2C%20the%20farmers'%20crisis%2C%20prices%20of%20onion%2C%20cotton%20and%20soybean%2C%20water%20scarcity%2C%20healthcare%2C%20road%20connectivity%2C%20and%20employment%20opportunities%20that%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20have%20been%20addressed%20by%20cabinet%20decisions%20but%20a%20lot%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20get%20the%20sentiment%20fully%20backing%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20functionary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729157640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fir2r4jdo_modi-shah_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthink-micro-act-inclusive-how-haryana-is-shaping-bjp-maharashtra-campaign-6809920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP's%20historic%20win%20in%20Haryana%20has%20prompted%20the%20party%20to%20approach%20Maharashtra%20elections%20with%20a%20far%20more%20confident%20strategy%20mainly%20centred%20around%20five%20important%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthink-micro-act-inclus