anna%20and%20nephew%20of%20senior%20Supreme%20Court%C2%A0judge%20Hansraj%20Khanna.%C2%A0He%20completed%20his%20schooling%20from%20Modern%20School%2C%20Barakhamba%20Road%20in%20Delhi%20and%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20his%20graduation%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%20in%201980.%20He%20then%20went%C2%A0%C2%A0on%20to%20pursue%20his%20law%20degree%20from%20DU's%20Campus%20Law%20Center.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJustice%20Hansraj%20Khanna%20had%20delivered%20the%20only%20dissenting%20judgment%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BHabeas%20Corpus%20case%26quot%3B%20of%20Additional%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Jabalpur%20vs%20Shivkant%20Shukla%20in%201976.%C2%A0Following%20this%2C%20the%20then%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20bypassed%20the%20seniority%20of%20four%20judges%20including%20the%20Justice%20Hansraj%20Khanna's%20and%20appointed%20Justice%20MH%20Beg%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20country%20in%20January%201977.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJustice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directly%20from%20his%20parent%20court%20-%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%C2%A0Since%201997%2C%20only%20six%20judges%20have%20been%20promoted%20from%20their%20parent%20High%20Court%20and%20appointed%20as%20judges%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0They%20include%20Justice%20Syed%20Abdul%20Nazeer%2C%20Justice%20Ranjana%20Prakash%20Desai%2C%20Justice%20Lokeshwar%20Singh%20Panta%2C%20Justice%20GP%20Mathur%2C%20Justice%20Ruma%20Pal%20and%20Justice%20SS%20Qadri.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Bar%20Council%20in%201983%2C%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20initially%20practised%20in%20the%20District%20Court%20at%20Delhi's%20Tis%20Hazari%20Complex%20and%20later%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20and%20tribunals%20in%20diverse%20fields%2C%20like%20constitutional%20law%2C%20direct%20taxation%2C%20arbitration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%C2%A0served%20a%20long%20tenure%20as%20Senior%20Standing%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20along%20with%20practice%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Commercial%20Law%2C%20Company%20Law%2C%20Land%20Law%2C%20Environmental%20Law%20and%20Medical%20Negligence.%C2%A0In%202004%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20Standing%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%C2%A0served%20as%20an%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20and%20Amicus%20Curiae%20in%20many%20criminal%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%20In%202005%2C%C2%A0Justice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20was%20promoted%20as%20Additional%20Judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20was%20appointed%20a%C2%A0permanent%20judge%20in%202006.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20being%20a%20judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20he%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Chairman%2FJudge-in-Charge%20of%20Delhi%20Judicial%20Academy%2C%20Delhi%20International%20Arbitration%20Centre%20and%20District%20Court%20Arbitration%20Centre.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJustice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20was%20promoted%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20on%20January%2018%2C%202019.%C2%A0Justice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%2C%20after%20taking%20oath%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20started%20his%20first%20day%20from%20the%20same%20court%20room%C2%A0from%20where%20his%20uncle%20Justice%20Hansraj%20Khanna%20had%20resigned%20and%20retired.%20The%20latter's%C2%A0photo%20is%20also%20hung%20in%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20per%20the%20rule%20of%20seniority%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20will%20serve%20as%20the%2051st%20CJI%20from%20November%2010%20for%20a%20period%20of%20six%20months.%C2%A0He%20will%20serve%20as%20CJI%20till%20May%2013%2C%202025%2C%C2%A0a%20day%20before%20his%2065th%20birthday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Chairman%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20Legal%20Services%20Committee%20from%20June%2017%2C%202023%20to%20December%2025%2C%202023.%20He%20is%C2%A0currently%20the%20Executive%20Chairman%20of%20National%20Legal%20Services%20Authority%20and%