2visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114309755%2Cimgsize-1062942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Finfosys-former-hr-head-mohandas-pai-to-government-why-are-you-ignoring-south-in-it-zoho-ceo-sridhar-vembu-responds-we-%2Farticleshow%2F114309682.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zoho%20CEO%20Sridhar%20Vembu%20responds%20to%20Mohandas%20Pai's%20criticism%20of%20the%20government's%20decision%20to%20establish%20AI%20Centres%20of%20Excellence%20in%20North%20India%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20selection%20process%20was%20thorough%20and%20unbiased%2C%20with%20strong%20proposals%20from%20the%20South%20considered%20but%20not%20chosen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Finfosys-former-hr-head-mohandas-pai-to-government-why-are-you-ignoring-south-in-it-zoho-ceo-sridhar-vembu-responds-we-%2Farticleshow%2F114309682.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Time%20In%2091%20Years%3A%20India%20Register%20Embarrassing%20Test%20Record%20vs%20New%20Zealand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMatt%20Henry%20and%20William%20O'Rourke%20picked%20nine%20wickets%20collectively%20to%20bowl%20out%20India%20for%20just%2046%20on%20day%20two%20of%20first%20Test%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20on%20Thursday.%20With%20this%2C%20India%20have%20now%20recorded%20their%20lowest%20total%20at%20home%20and%20third%20lowest%20Test%20score%20overall.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20in%2091%20years%20(since%20India's%20first%20home%20Test%20in%201931)%20that%20they%20scored%20less%20than%2050%20in%20an%20innings.%20Under%20overcast%20condition%2C%20Henry%20exhibited%20great%20control%20on%20line%20and%20length%20to%20pick%205-15%20and%20also%20reached%20the%20landmark%20of%20100%20Test%20wickets.%20O'Rourke%2C%20playing%20in%20his%20first%20Test%20in%20India%2C%20made%20a%20fantastic%20impression%20with%20his%20awkward%20bounce%20and%20mixing%20of%20lengths%20to%20pick%204-22%20while%20veteran%20pacer%20Tim%20Southee%20took%20a%20scalp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20right%20from%20them%20electing%20to%20bat%20first%20amidst%20downpour%20threats%2C%20things%20backfired%20spectacularly.%20With%20no%20grass%20on%20the%20pitch%2C%20they%20picked%20three%20spinners%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20this%20season%2C%20with%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20being%20the%20only%20pacers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20conditions%20heavily%20favouring%20an%20accurate%20New%20Zealand%20bowling%20line-up%20and%20backed%20up%20brilliantly%20by%20their%20fielders%2C%20India%20didn't%20show%20the%20desired%20batting%20application%20to%20grind%20it%20out%20against%20swing%20or%20seam%20and%20fell%20without%20doing%20much.%20Only%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(20)%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(13)%20reached%20double%20figures%20in%20a%20sorry%20Indian%20batting%20show%20laced%20with%20five%20ducks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20far%20from%20his%20fluent%20best%20and%20even%20survived%20an%20lbw%20appeal%20on%20umpire's%20call%20off%20Matt%20Henry.%20But%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20step%20out%20against%20a%20masterly%20Tim%20Southee%2C%20Rohit%20was%20castled%20through%20the%20gate%20while%20going%20for%20a%20big%20drive%20against%20the%20inswinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli's%20surprising%20promotion%20to%20number%20three%2C%20after%20Shubman%20Gill%20was%20ruled%20out%20due%20to%20neck%20stiffness%2C%20earned%20him%20vociferous%20chants%20from%20the%20sparse%20crowd%20at%20his%20adopted%20home%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20brought%20to%20a%20quick%20end%20when%20O'Rourke%20got%20extra%20bounce%20on%20a%20nip-backer%20which%20Kohli%20looked%20to%20defend%2C%20but%20it%20took%20the%20glove%20edge%20to%20forward%20leaping%20Glenn%20Phillips%20at%20leg-gully%2C%20as%20he%20departed%20for%20a%20nine-ball%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20trouble%20followed%20India%20as%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20tried%20to%20counterattack%20with%20a%20forceful%20lofted%20drive%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20mis-hitting%20off%20Henry%20to%20Devon%20Conway%20at%20mid-off%2C%20who%20stuck%20out%20his%20right%20hand%20and%20took%20a%20stunning%20catch.%20Pant%20was%20a%20curious%20mix%20of%20caution%20and%20aggressiveness%2C%20including%20trying%20to%20reverse-sweep%20off%20Henry%2C%20before%20rain%20brought%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20play%20resumed%20at%2011%3A05am%2C%20Pant%20and%20Jaiswal%20got%20a%20boundary%20each%20to%20try%20and%20rebuild%20India's%20innings.%20But%20O'Rourke%20struck%20again%20as%20Jaiswal%20went%20hard%20on%20the%20cut%20and%20was%20caught%20brilliantly%20by%20backward%20point%20diving%20low%20to%20his%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20brought%20two%20for%20the%20pacer%20as%20he%20strangled%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20supposed%20to%20bat%20at%20three%2C%20down%20leg%20for%20a%20six-ball%20duck%2C%20and%20was%20followed%20by%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20being%20bizarrely%20too%20early%20into%20the%20flick%20and%20gave%20a%20high%20leading%20edge%20to%20backward%20point%20off%20Henry%20as%20New%20Zealand%20walked%20off%20the%20field%20as%20the%20happier%20side%20at%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20lunch%2C%20Henry%20struck%20on%20the%20very%20first%20ball%20by%20catching%20shoulder%20edge%20of%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20the%20ball%20lobbed%20to%20gully.%20He%20then%20enticed%20Pant%20into%20tentative%20defence%20and%20edged%20to%20second%20slip.%20O'Rourke%20had%20Bumrah%20heaving%20to%20long%20leg%2C%20before%20Henry%20ended%20the%20Indian%20batting%20horror%20show%20by%20having%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20caught%20at%20gully%20to%20cap%20off%20a%20brilliant%20time%20for%20New%20Zealand%20with%20the%20red%20cherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729153740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Feh6p