pulmonary%20Resuscitation%20(CPR).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYash%20Tadvi%2C%20a%20wildlife%20rescuer%20in%20Gujarat's%20Vadodara%2C%20said%20he%20received%20a%20call%20on%20his%20helpline%20number%20about%20a%20snake%20being%20found%20dead%20in%20an%20area.%20Upon%20reaching%20the%20location%2C%20he%20said%20he%20saw%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20reptile%2C%20a%20one-foot%20non-venomous%20checkered%20keelback%2C%20and%20believed%20that%20it%20would%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20there%2C%20the%20snake%20was%20in%20an%20unconscious%20state.%20There%20was%20no%20movement%2C%20but%20I%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20snake%20would%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tadvi%20said%20after%20the%20miraculous%20save%2C%20which%20was%20recorded%20on%20a%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20took%20its%20neck%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20opened%20its%20mouth%20and%20tried%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20consciousness%20by%20blowing%20into%20its%20mouth%20for%20three%20minutes.%20Even%20after%20giving%20CPR%20in%20the%20first%20two%20attempts%2C%20there%20was%20no%20change%20in%20its%20condition.%20However%2C%20when%20I%20gave%20CPR%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20it%20started%20moving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snake%20has%20now%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20forest%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729153620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fgfjp40c8_gujarat-snake_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-gujarat-man-saves-snakes-life-by-performing-cpr-6809389%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Gujarat%20has%20saved%20a%20snake%20by%20performing%20the%20life-saving%20technique%20known%20as%20Cardiopulmonary%20Resuscitation%20(CPR).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22