ps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-court-issues-arrest-warrant-for-ex-pm-sheikh-hasina%2Farticleshow%2F114309285.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-court-issues-arrest-warrant-for-ex-pm-sheikh-hasina%2Famp_articleshow%2F114309285.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-court-issues-arrest-warrant-for-ex-pm-sheikh-hasina%2Famp_articleshow%2F114309285.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nayab%20Saini%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20PM%2C%20Key%20NDA%20Allies%20Present%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%2054%2C%20took%20oath%20as%20Haryana's%20Chief%20Minister%20today%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20marking%20the%20BJP's%20record%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0The%20oath-taking%20ceremony%2C%20held%20at%20Panchkula's%20Parade%20Ground%20near%20Chandigarh%2C%20was%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20top%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20along%20with%2018%20Chief%20Ministers%20from%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mega%20political%20gathering%20comes%20just%20ahead%20of%20crucial%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20and%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20Governor%20Bandaru%20Dattatreya%20administered%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20and%20secrecy%20to%20Mr%20Saini%2C%20who%20first%20assumed%20the%20chief%20minister's%20role%20in%20March%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20replacing%20former%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%C2%A0Besides%20Mr%20Saini%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20Krishan%20Lal%20Panwar%20and%20Rao%20Narbir%20Singh%20were%20among%20those%20who%20were%20administered%20the%20oath%20of%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini's%20political%20journey%20spans%20nearly%2030%20years.%20Born%20in%201970%2C%20he%20entered%20politics%20under%20the%20mentorship%20of%20Mr%20Khattar.%20Mr%20Saini%20was%20first%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20Naraingarh%20in%202014%20and%20later%20inducted%20into%20the%20state%20Cabinet%20in%202016.%20His%20rise%20to%20prominence%20came%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Kurukshetra%2C%20a%20seat%20he%20won%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20by%20defeating%20Congress's%20Nirmal%20Singh%20by%20a%20significant%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20swearing-in%2C%20Mr%20Saini%20undertook%20a%20series%20of%20religious%20visits%2C%20paying%20his%20respects%20at%20the%20Valmiki%20Bhawan%2C%20a%20local%20gurdwara%2C%20and%20the%20Mansa%20Devi%20temple%20in%20Panchkula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20defied%20the%20odds%20to%20secure%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20Haryana.%20In%20the%20October%205%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20achieved%20an%20unprecedented%20victory%2C%20securing%2048%20of%20the%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20The%20Congress%2C%20the%20principal%20opposition%2C%20managed%20to%20win%2037%20seats%2C%20while%20smaller%20regional%20parties%20like%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20failed%20to%20make%20any%20significant%20impact.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20once%20a%20formidable%20political%20force%2C%20was%20reduced%20to%20just%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini's%20victory%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20came%20from%20Ladwa%2C%20a%20constituency%20created%20in%202007.%20He%20won%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2016%2C054%20votes%2C%20defeating%20Congress%20candidate%20Mewa%20Singh.%20While%20eight%20of%20the%20ten%20ministers%20from%20his%20previous%20Cabinet%20faced%20defeat%2C%20the%20two%20who%20won%20were%20Mahipal%20Dhanda