Of%20B-2%20Bombers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20B-2%20Spirit%20bomber%2C%20known%20for%20its%20stealth%20capabilities%20and%20heavy%20payload%2C%20is%20capable%20of%20delivering%20a%20far%20greater%20volume%20of%20ordnance%20compared%20to%20fighter%20jets.%20The%20B-2%20offers%20the%20US%20military%20an%20unparalleled%20ability%20to%20strike%20high-value%20targets%20that%20are%20either%20deeply%20fortified%20or%20well-concealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Austin%20explained%20that%20the%20strikes%20were%20authorised%20at%20the%20direction%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20unique%20demonstration%20of%20the%20United%20States'%20ability%20to%20target%20facilities%20that%20our%20adversaries%20seek%20to%20keep%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20deeply%20buried%20or%20fortified%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Austin%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20Regional%20Tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20the%20strikes%20comes%20amid%20heightened%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20with%20US%20allies%2C%20particularly%20Israel%2C%20facing%20ongoing%20threats%20from%20Iran%20and%20its%20various%20regional%20proxies.%20The%20Houthis%2C%20operating%20from%20Yemen%2C%20have%20consistently%20launched%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping%20and%20military%20vessels%2C%20disrupting%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20critical%20maritime%20trade%20routes.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20these%20attacks%20have%20escalated%2C%20with%20the%20group%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20launching%20ballistic%20and%20cruise%20missiles%20as%20well%20as%20drones%20against%20US%20Navy%20ships%20and%20international%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis'%20activities%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%20targeting%20vessels%20with%20weaponry%20that%20originated%20from%20these%20underground%20storage%20sites%2C%20have%20raised%20alarms%20about%20the%20security%20of%20global%20trade%20routes%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20environmental%20catastrophes.%20In%20August%2C%20a%20Greek-flagged%20vessel%20came%20under%20attack%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20oil%20spill%20and%20serious%20environmental%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20Houthis%20escalated%20their%20campaign%2C%20launching%20approximately%20two%20dozen%20ballistic%20and%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20as%20well%20as%20drones%2C%20aimed%20at%20three%20US%20Navy%20destroyers.%20Although%20none%20of%20these%20missiles%20struck%20their%20targets%2C%20the%20attacks%20prompted%20increased%20military%20activity%20from%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHouthi%20Attacks%20Tied%20To%20Regional%20Conflicts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran-backed%20Houthis%20have%20framed%20their%20actions%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20alignment%20with%20groups%20like%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%2C%20who%20are%20actively%20engaged%20in%20ongoing%20conflicts%20with%20Israel.%20Following%20an%20attempted%20missile%20strike%20deep%20inside%20Israel%20in%20September%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20openly%20declared%20their%20support%20for%20these%20groups.%20While%20the%20missile%20ultimately%20fragmented%20in%20mid-air%20and%20caused%20no%20injuries%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20warned%20the%20Houthis%20would%20%26quot%3Bpay%20a%20heavy%20price%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20actions.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20targeted%20Houthi%20positions%20in%20Yemen%20shortly%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouthis-israel-yemen-how-yemens-houthi-rebels-get-hold-of-ballistic-missiles-to-attack-israel-6576154%5C%22%3EHow%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20Rebels%20Got%20Hold%20Of%20Ballistic%20Missiles%20To%20Attack%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20weeks%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20continued%20launching%20missiles%20and%20drones%20toward%20Israel%2C%20further%20complicating%20the%20regional%20security%20landscape.%20These%20actions%2C%20combined%20with%20continued%20Houthi%20assaults%20on%20international%20shipping%2C%20have%20drawn%20significant%20military%20responses%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20strike%20on%20Houthi%20facilities%20adds%20to%20a%20series%20of%20US%20military%20actions%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20the%20Houthis'%20growing%20arsenal%20and%20degrading%20their%20operational%20capabilities.%20US%20Central%20Command%20(CENTCOM)%20confirmed%20that%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20civilian%20casualties%20from%20the%20latest%20strikes.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20US%20has%20increased%20its%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20the%20deployment%20of%20advanced%20naval%20assets%20such%20as%20carrier%20strike%20groups%2C%20amphibious%20ready%20groups%2C%20and%20guided%20missile%20destroyers%2C%20along%20with%20air%20support%20in%20the%20form%20of%20fighter%20jets%20and%20attack%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729148280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F4843vf98_b2-bomber-afp-_625x300_17_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-us-uses-advanced-b-2-stealth-bombers-against-houthis-in-yemen-6808836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20airstrikes%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20targeting%20key%20underground%20weapons%20storage%20facilities%20controlled%20by%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-us-uses-advanced-b-2-stealth-bombers-against-houthis-in-yemen-6808836%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20kills%20153%20people%20after%20fuel%20tanker%20crash%20in%20Nigeria%22%2C%