20uncapped%20cricketer%20but%20in%20that%20scenario%2C%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20use%20the%20Right%20To%20Match%20(RTM)%20on%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tim%20David%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111686-tim-david-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETim%20David%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20try%20to%20buy%20Indian%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20mega%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20five-time%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20have%20appointed%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20as%20their%20bowling%20coach%2C%20said%20the%20franchise%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20MI%20said%20Mhambrey%2C%20who%20was%20India's%20bowling%20coach%20from%20November%202021%20till%20their%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20in%20June%2C%20will%20work%20along%20with%20current%20bowling%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lasith%20Malinga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F639-lasith-malinga-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELasith%20Malinga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20coaching%20team%20under%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahela%20Jayawardene%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F244-mahela-jayawardene-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMahela%20Jayawardene%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20Mhambrey's%20second%20stint%20at%20MI%20after%20previously%20being%20part%20of%20the%20support%20staff%20when%20they%20won%C2%A0IPL%C2%A02013%2C%20Champions%20League%20T20%20(2011%2C%202013)%2C%20a%20runner%20up%20finish%20(2010)%20and%20two%20more%20playoffs%20appearances%20in%20the%C2%A0IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMhambrey%2C%20who%20was%20discovered%20by%20the%20BCA%20Mafatlal%20Bowling%20scheme%20under%20English%20fast%20bowling%20great%20Frank%20Tyson%20in%201990%2C%20played%20two%20Tests%20and%20three%20ODIs%20for%20India%20from%201996%20to%201998.%20But%20he%20had%20an%20illustrious%20domestic%20cricket%20career%20with%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20became%20a%20member%20of%20winning%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20five%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20holds%20a%20Level%203%20coaching%20diploma%20from%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20and%20served%20as%20coach%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Baroda%2C%20Vidarbha%20(2016-17)%20and%20Bengal%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20before%20entering%20the%20national%20set-up%20%E2%80%93%20first%20as%20India%20A%20and%20U19%20sides%20coach%2C%20then%20becoming%20a%20trusted%20member%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20coaching%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMhambrey%20also%20coached%20India%20U19%20team%20to%20runners-up%20finish%20in%20the%202020%20U19%20World%20Cup%20in%20South%20Africa.%20He%20earned%20widespread%20acclaim%20for%20his%20time%20with%20the%20senior%20Indian%20team%2C%20where%20India%20emerged%20as%20a%20menacing%20bowling%20line-up%2C%20via%20thorough%20analysis%2C%20man-management%20skills%20and%20solid%20tactical%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20got%20special%20acknowledgement%20for%20his%20hardwork%20and%20motivation%20from%20senior%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20on%20home%20soil%2C%20by%20placing%20the%20ball%20on%20his%20head%20while%20taking%20a%20five-fer%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20IANS%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729147620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpo358do8_rohit-sharma-ipl-bcci_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frohit-sharma-to-leave-mumbai-indians-ahead-of-ipl2025-auction-report-provides-explosive-update-6807903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20surrounding%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20future%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202025%20Auction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frohit-sharma-to-leave-mumbai-indians-ahead-of-ipl2025-auction-report-provides-explosive-update-6807903%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India-Canada%20Showdown%3A%20When%20Fiction%20Is%20As%20Important%20As%20Facts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fcbi4u6gg_justin_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20so%20different%2C%20you%20and%20I.%20We've%20both%20spent%20our%20lives%20looking%20for%20the%20weakness%20in%20one%20another's%20systems.%20Don't%20you%20think%20it's%20time%20to%20recognize%20there%20is%20as%20little%20worth%20on%20your%20side%20as%20there%20is%20on%20mine%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who've%20been%20rooting%20for%20Gary%20Oldman%20playing%20Jackson%20Lamb%2C%20the%20instantly%20unlikeable%20boss%20of%20the%20good-for-nothings%20of%20MI5%2C%20the%20British%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20in%20Apple's%20%3Cem%3ESlow%20Horses%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20may%20not%20even%20remember%20this%20line%20the%20actor%20delivered%20playing%20another%20spy%20boss%20in%20another%20spy%20thriller%3A%20as%20George%20Smiley%20in%3Cem%3E%20Tinker%20Tailor%20Soldier%20Spy%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%202011%20film%20based%20on%20John%20la%20Carre's%20book.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressed%20to%20Smiley's%20Russian%20counterpart%2C%20Karla%2C%20this%20line%2C%20emblematic%20of%20the%20film's%20politics%2C%20was%20celebrated%20and%20decried%20in%20equal%20measure%20for%20creating%20an%20equivalence%20between%20the%20US%20and%20the%20USSR%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%20Going%20by%20the%20recent%20media%20stories%20and%20diplomatic%20activity%2C%20George%20Smiley%20could%20have%20very%20well%20said%20it%20about%20India%20and%20Canada%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlow%20Hot%2C%20Blow%20Cold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20have%20expelled%20each%20other's%20top%20diplomats%2C%20following%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister's%20latest%20accusation%20of%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20being%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%20India%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20not%20only%20denied%20it%20but%20also%20mounted%20a%20counterattack%20on%20Canada%20for%20nurturing%20anti-India%20groups%20within%20its%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFall%20is%20not%20fair%20weather%20for%20India-Canada%20relations.%20Exactly%20one%20year%20ago%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20were%20engaged%20in%20similar%20diplomatic%20acrimony%20over%20the%20same%20assassination.%20Khalistan%2C%20after%20nuclear%20proliferation%2C%20has%20been%20their%20proverbial%20bee%20in%20the%20bonnet%20for%20several%20decades.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20lull%20during%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20stayed%20alive%20and%20volatile.%20It%20is%20not%20going%20anywhere%20in%20a%20hurry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20soft%20approach%20towards%20anti-India%20outfits%20was%20once%20attributed%20solely%20to%20its%20domestic%20politics%3A%20the%20country%20is%20home%20to%20the%20largest%20Sikh%20diaspora%2C%20with%20around%207%2C70%2C000%20of%20them%20living%20there.%20The%20current%20strain%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%20however%2C%20may%20not%20just%20be%20about%20Canada's%20vote%20bank%20politics%20or%20India's%20internal%20affairs%20involving%20resistance%20from%20a%20sect%20of%20Sikhs.%20There%20is%2C%20quite%20clearly%2C%20an%20emergence%20of%20bilateral%20antagonism%20now.%20Are%20the%20rapprochement%20personnel%20doing%20their%20job%20well%3F%20Or%2C%20more%20provocatively%2C%20are%20the%20spies%20doing%20theirs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlashbacks%20From%201975%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealistically%20speaking%2C%20assassinations%20on%20foreign%20soil%20are%20not%20a%20no-go%20zone%2C%20even%20with%20declared%20enemies%2C%20if%20the%20assassins%20are%20smart.%20The%20morality%20and%20legality%20of%20such%20actions%20is%20another%20story.%20What%2C%20then%2C%20has%20compelled%20Canada%2C%20a%20limited%20ally%2C%20to%20make%20public%20its%20investigations%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20assassination%20case%20and%20hold%20India%20responsible%3F%20Has%20there%20been%20a%20slight%20or%20a%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20intended%20or%20otherwise%2C%20behind%20the%20scenes%20that%20a%20public%20show%20is%20to%20be%20put%20up%3F%20Are%20there%20bad-faith%20actors%20at%20work%20on%20either%20side%2C%20or%20is%20it%20sheer%20incompetence%3F%20It%20could%20be%20either%20or%20both%2C%20but%20as%20venerable%20Canadian%20writer%20Margaret%20Atwood%20reminds%20us%2C%20%26quot%3BStupidity%20is%20the%20same%20as%20evil%20if%20you%20judge%20by%20the%20results%26quot%3B.%20Therefore%2C%20it's%20the%20breakdown%20of%20bilateral%20ties%20that%20matters%2C%20much%20more%20than%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20what%20caused%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20escalation%20of%20diplomatic%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20is%20beginning%20to%20loosely%20resemble%20another%20controversial%20diplomatic%20event%20that%20occurred%20half%20a%20century%20ago%3A%20the%20breakdown%20of%20the%20then%20newly%20forged%20Australia-North%20Korea%20relations.%20On%20October%2030%2C%201975%2C%20Pyongyang%20recalled%20its%20diplomats%20from%20Canberra%2C%20citing%20the%20host%20country's%20'unfriendly%20attitude'%20and%20'intolerable%20provocative%20acts'%20in%20a%20communication%20sent%20via%20commercial%20mail.%20Less%20than%20ten%20days%20later%2C%20Australian%20diplomats%20were%20ousted%20from%20Pyongyang%20on%20November%208%20on%20account%20of%20'unfriendly%20behaviour'%20and%20'abuse%20of%20diplomatic%20immunity'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actors%20and%20the%20times%20are%20different%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20is%20the%20same.%20This%20inability%20to%20smoothen%20out%20the%20rough%20edges%20time%20and%20again%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20the%20political%20and%20diplomatic%20leaders%20of%20India%20and%20Canada.%20What%20are%20long%20bilateral%20ties%20worth%20if%20they%20cannot%20withstand%20such%20events%3F%20Both%20Ottawa%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20engaged%20in%20the%20game%20of%20provocation%20and%20reconciliation.%20The%20classic%20blow-hot%2C%20blow-cold%20approach.%20To%20what%20end%2C%20though%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Lesson%20From%3Cem%3E%20Bridge%20Of%20Spies%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20George%20Smiley's%20wisdom%2C%20looking%20for%20weaknesses%20in%20the%20other%20is%20a%20zero-sum%20game.%20This%20isn't%20the%20Cold%20War%20yet%2C%20but%20as%20India%20grows%20in%20stature%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20this%20game%20intensifying%20will%20increase%20correspondingly.%20India%20and%20Canada%20are%20not%20directly%20engaged%20in%20any%20military-territorial%20jostling%2C%20so%20these%20flare-ups%20have%20an%20even%20more%20limited%20scope.%20Both%20are%20citing%20long-term%20national%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20other%20countries%20like%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20US%20are%20trying%20to%20broker%20'peace'%20by%20urging%20India%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomacy%20is%20an%20exercise%20in%20sifting%20fact%20from%20fiction%20but%20addressing%20both%20because%20both%20matter%2C%20even%20if%20unequally.%20Another%20popular%20culture%20reference%20to%20demonstrate%20it%20comes%20from%20%3Cem%3EBridge%20of%20Spies%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%202014%20film%20about%20the%20famous%20spy%20exchange%20between%20the%20US%20and%20USSR.%20James%20Donovan%20(Tom%20Hanks)%2C%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20a%20Russian%20spy%20called%20Rudolf%20Abel%20(Mark%20Rylance)%2C%20tells%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20case%20against%20you%20matters.%20Making%20them%20prove%20it%20matters.%20The%20fiction%20is%3A%20whether%20you%20did%20it%20or%20not%20doesn't%20matter.%20The%20state%20has%20to%20prove%20it%2C%20that%20you're%20a%20spy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20anyone%20condescends%20about%20taking%20lessons%20from%20fiction%2C%20remember%2C%20apart%20from%20John%20la%20Carre%2C%20celebrated%20writers%20like%20Ian%20Fleming%20and%20Graham%20Greene%20once%20served%20in%20MI6.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729147260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fkkm9j03o_justin_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-canada-row-when-fiction-is-as-important-as-facts-6808464%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20has%20compelled%20Canada%20to%20make%20public%20its%20investigations%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20assassination%20case%20and%20hold%20India%20responsible%3F%20Has%20there%20been%20a%20slight%20or%20a%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20intended%20or%20otherwise%2C%20behind%20the%20scenes%20that%20a%20public%20show%20is%20to%20be%20put%20up%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-canada-row-when-fiction-is-as-important-as-facts-6808464%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2