%2Fmystery-tar-balls-wash-up-on-sydney-beaches-forcing-seven-to-close-13234983%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmystery-tar-balls-wash-up-on-sydney-beaches-forcing-seven-to-close-13234983%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teenage%20guns%20for%20hire%3A%20Swedish%20gangs%20targeting%20Israeli%20interests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729145213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F67fc%2Flive%2F32dc66b0-8bf8-11ef-b6b0-c9af5f7f16e4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1e85l701y3o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gangs%20may%20be%20behind%20the%20recent%20attacks%20but%20Sweden%20believes%20Iran%20has%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1e85l701y3o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1e85l701y3o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1e85l701y3o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2265%20Bullets%2C%20YouTube%20Videos%2C%20Bikes%3A%20How%20Baba%20Siddique%20Murder%20Was%20Planned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20into%20the%20murder%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbaba-siddique-murder%5C%22%3EBaba%20Siddique%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20revealed%20details%20of%20the%20planning%20behind%20the%20operation%20which%20included%20the%20acquisition%20of%20a%20substantial%20cache%20of%20bullets%2C%20YouTube%20firearms%20training%2C%20and%20the%20careful%20orchestration%20of%20getaway%20plans.%20The%20plotters%20aimed%20to%20ensure%20the%20murder%20was%20executed%20with%20precision%2C%20taking%20no%20chances%20on%20ammunition%20or%20escape%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20four%20individuals%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20including%20Haryana%20resident%20Gurmail%20Baljit%20Singh%20(23)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20native%20Dharmaraj%20Rajesh%20Kashyap%20(19)%2C%20both%20alleged%20shooters%3B%20Harishkumar%20Balakram%20Nisad%20(23)%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bco-conspirator%26quot%3B%20Pravin%20Lonkar%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENisad%20and%20Kashyap%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20village%20as%20the%20wanted%20accused%20Shivkumar%20Gautam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20the%20accused%20responsible%20for%20Mr%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbaba-siddique%5C%22%3ESiddique%3C%2Fa%3E's%20murder%20-%20Gurmail%20Singh%20(23)%20and%20Dharamaraj%20Kashyap%20(19)%20-%20were%20equipped%20with%2065%20bullets%2C%20a%20stockpile%20intended%20to%20guarantee%20they%20would%20not%20run%20out%20of%20ammunition.%20Six%20of%20these%20bullets%20were%20fired%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%2012%2C%20when%20Mr%20Siddique%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20his%20son%20Zeeshan%20Siddique's%20office%20in%20the%20Nirmal%20Nagar%20area%20in%20Bandra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20recovered%20two%20firearms%20used%20by%20the%20accused%20-%20an%20Austrian-made%20pistol%20and%20a%20locally%20manufactured%20country-made%20pistol.%20Alongside%20these%20weapons%2C%20police%20found%2028%20live%20bullets%20on%20Singh%20and%20Kashyap%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20arrest.%20The%20investigative%20team%20also%20discovered%20a%20black%20bag%2C%20located%20just%20a%20short%20distance%20from%20the%20murder%20site%2C%20containing%20a%20Turkish-made%207.62%20bore%20pistol%20and%2030%20live%20rounds.%20This%20bag%20also%20held%20two%20Aadhar%20cards%20-%20one%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Shivkumar%20Gautam%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20suspect%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20another%20under%20the%20name%20Sumit%20Kumar%2C%20though%20both%20cards%20bore%20Shivkumar's%20photo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotorbike%20Plan%20Foiled%20By%20Accident%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20had%20initially%20planned%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack%20using%20a%20motorbike.%20The%20idea%20was%20for%20the%20shooters%20to%20ride%20up%20to%20the%20location%2C%20execute%20the%20murder%2C%20and%20then%20escape%20quickly%20by%20bike.%20However%2C%20a%20traffic%20accident%20involving%20two%20of%20the%20suspects%20caused%20them%20to%20abandon%20this%20plan.%20Instead%2C%20the%20three%20perpetrators%20decided%20to%20travel%20by%20auto-rickshaw%20to%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crime.%20After%20the%20murder%2C%20they%20quickly%20changed%20their%20clothes%20to%20avoid%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishkumar%20Balakram%20Nisad%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arrested%20co-conspirators%2C%20had%20transferred%20Rs%2060%2C000%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20a%20motorbike.%20Out%20of%20this%20amount%2C%20Rs%2032%2C000%20was%20used%20to%20buy%20a%20second-hand%20bike%2C%20which%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EManhunt%20And%20Escape%20Attempts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20the%20involvement%20of%20several%20suspects%2C%20with%20the%20prime%20accused%2C%20Shubham%20Lonkar%2C%20an%20alleged%20member%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-baba-siddique-roster-of-700-shooters-parallels-to-d-company-how-lawrence-bishnoi-operates-6786815%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20is%20still%20at%20large.%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20issued%20a%20Look%20Out%20Circular%20(LOC)%20against%20Lonkar%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20attempting%20to%20flee%20to%20Nepal.%20His%20photographs%20have%20been%20circulated%20at%20the%20Nepal%20border%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20his%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELonkar%20had%20remained%20active%20on%20social%20media%20until%20just%20three%20days%20before%20the%20murder%2C%20with%20responsibility%20for%20Mr%20Siddique's%20killing%20reportedly%20being%20claimed%20via%20his%20Facebook%20profile%20on%20October%209.%20His%20brother%2C%20Praveen%20Lonkar%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20providing%20financial%20support%20to%20the%20killers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20not%20yet%20managed%20to%20track%20down%20Shubham's%20exact%20location%2C%20but%20intelligence%20suggests%20he%20may%20have%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20key%20criminal%20networks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouTube%20Training%20And%20Firearm%20Mastery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20shooters%20learned%20to%20operate%20guns%20by%20watching%20YouTube%20tutorials.%20In%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20murder%2C%20the%20accused%20rented%20a%20house%20in%20the%20Kurla%20area%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20they%20practised%20loading%2C%20unloading%2C%20and%20handling%20weapons.%20Due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20open%20space%2C%20they%20engaged%20in%20%26quot%3Bdry%20practice%26quot%3B%20drills%20and%20rehearsing%20with%20unloaded%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20also%20revealed%20that%20Shivkumar%20Gautam%2C%20another%20prime%20suspect%2C%20had%20experience%20with%20firearms%20from%20celebratory%20firings%20at%20weddings%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20he%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20honed%20his%20shooting%20skills.%20Gautam%2C%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20shooter%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20only%20participated%20in%20the%20planning%20but%20also%20trained%20Kashyap%20and%20Singh%20in%20the%20handling%20of%20guns.%20The%20trio%20communicated%20frequently%20via%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20Snapchat%20and%20Instagram%2C%20using%20these%20apps%20to%20stay%20under%20police%20radar%20while%20coordinating%20the%20assassination%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubham%20Lonkar%2C%20the%20key%20suspect%20on%20the%20run%2C%20was%20previously%20arrested%20in%20January%20under%20the%20Arms%20Act%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Akola%20district