his%20safe%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%20We%20start%20by%20hiring%20members%20who%20we%20have%20an%20inkling%20will%20be%20good%20with%20animals%2C%20and%20bring%20some%20love%20and%20care%20to%20the%20work.%20Then%20we%20set%20examples%20and%20policies%20to%20encourage%20those%20attitudes%2C%20and%20our%20managers%20are%20constantly%20training%20in%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20such%20care.%20We%20give%20each%20dog%20a%20name%20and%20keep%20a%20paper%20record%20of%20each%20one%20with%20its%20picture%20on%20the%20page.%20The%20team%20members%20use%20the%20names%2C%20and%20converse%20with%20each%20other%20about%20the%20progress%20the%20dogs%20are%20making%2C%20the%20medications%20they%20are%20taking%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20all%20team%20members%20as%20many%20different%20duties%20as%20possible%3A%20feeding%2C%20administering%20medicines%2C%20cleaning%20cages%20and%20pens%2C%20keeping%20records%20of%20care%2C%20maintaining%20infrastructure%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20going%20out%20for%20rescues%2C%20etc.%20Everyone%20is%20encouraged%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20dogs%2C%20examine%20their%20bodies%20for%20any%20new%20problems%2C%20cuddle%20with%20them%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20So%2C%20a%20member%20who%20may%20not%20have%20experience%20with%20hands-on%20dog%20care%20will%20learn%20it%20by%20the%20good%20examples%20set%20by%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20of%20mass%20feeding%20stray%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20initiatives%20taken%20by%20Semchan%20is%20the%20feeding%20of%20dogs%20not%20just%20housed%20at%20the%20rescue%20shelter%20but%20across%20different%20feeding%20centres%20in%20Leh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feed%20about%20300%20dogs%20in%20the%20summer%20months%20and%20in%20the%20last%20winter%20season%2C%20we%20fed%20about%20650%20(one%20feeding%20session%20a%20day)%20across%2027%20feeding%20stations.%20We%20prepare%20the%20food%20in%20our%20kitchen%2C%20consisting%20of%20rice%20mixed%20with%20dry%20dog%20food%2C%20chicken%2C%20and%20a%20water%2Fmilk%20portion%20to%20soften%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20canine%20experts%20have%20expressed%20their%20concern%20about%20mass%20feeding%2C%20and%20how%20it%20exacerbates%20the%20growing%20conflict%20between%20dogs%20and%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20past%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319519%2Fwhy-india-struggles-to-deal-with-street-stray-dogs-animal-rights-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Abi%20Tamim%20Vanak%2C%20an%20animal%20ecologist%20and%20conservation%20biologist%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20%5Bnecessarily%5D%20provocation%2C%20but%20pack%20formation%20that%20leads%20to%20deadly%20%5Bstray%20dog%5D%20attacks%20on%20people.%20And%20why%20does%20pack%20formation%20happen%3F%20It%20happens%20whenever%20you%20have%20massive%20resources%20gathered%20in%20one%20place.%20Feeding%20one%20or%20two%20dogs%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20when%20you%20feed%20five%2C%20seven%2C%20or%20ten%20dogs%20at%20one%20location%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20pack%20formation%20occurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeena%2C%20however%2C%20disagrees%20with%20this%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescued%20stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERescued%20stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHungry%20dogs%20become%20aggressive%20dogs.%20In%20our%20experience%2C%20feeding%20helps%20in%20keeping%20the%20dog%20population%20calm%20and%20content%20and%20does%20not%20encourage%20attacks.%20If%20there%20had%20been%20any%20attacks%20on%20humans%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20we%20feed%2C%20the%20Government%20would%20have%20contacted%20us.%20We%20have%20not%20received%20any%20such%20notification.%20During%20winter%2C%20we%20feed%20between%201%20pm%20and%205%20pm%20so%20that%20the%20dogs%20are%20not%20hungry%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20amid%20rising%20dog%20bite%20cases%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Union%20Territory%20Government%20of%20Ladakh%20issued%20an%20order%20in%20July%202024%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20armed%20forces%20establishments%2C%20hotels%2C%20homestays%2C%20restaurants%2C%20guest%20houses%20in%20Leh%20district%20shall%20strictly%20refrain%20from%20throwing%20leftover%20foods%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20other%20places%20reachable%20by%20feral%20dogs.%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20given%20for%20this%20order%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccases%20of%20feral%20dog%20bites%20have%20gone%20up%20exponentially%2C%20thereby%20posing%20a%20risk%20to%20public%20safety%20and%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMass%20feeding%20is%20a%20delicate%20issue%20that%20requires%20greater%20scientific%20scrutiny%20and%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommitment%20to%20dog%20care%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20paying%20for%20food%20and%20the%20fuel%20costs%20incurred%20during%20rescues%2C%20Semchen%20also%20incurs%20the%20cost%20of%20spaying%20and%20sterilising%20dogs%20via%20a%20private%20vet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20a%20Vet%20Tech%20comes%20every%20evening%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20to%20bandage%20the%20dogs.%20They%20also%20obtain%20vaccines%20to%20protect%20dogs%20from%20the%20Parvovirus%20%5Ba%20highly%20contagious%20disease%20that%20can%20affect%20dogs%5D%20that%20come%20in%20from%20Pune.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20no%20cases%20of%20Parvo%20since%20March-April%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20is%20a%20strong%20commitment%20to%20care%20and%20rehabilitation%20at%20Semchan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%