%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20their%20opinion%2C%20scanty%20or%20normal%20menstruation%20indicates%20that%20the%20blood%20is%20collecting%20in%20the%20uterus%2C%20forming%20lumps%2C%20and%20will%20eventually%20impinge%20on%20their%20vital%20organs%20and%20cause%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20proper%20diagnoses%20extends%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20as%20well%2C%20she%20figured.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20we%20started%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116337%2Fgood-news-india-averted-million-child-deaths-since-2005%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20rate%20was%20121%20per%201%2C000%20(indicating%20that%20121%20out%20of%201%2C000%20children%20would%20die%20before%20reaching%20the%20first%20year%20of%20life).%20The%20number%20one%20cause%20was%20childhood%20pneumonia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20she%20along%20with%20Dr%20Abhay%20trained%20the%20village%20health%20workers%20to%20diagnose%20and%20treat%20the%20condition.%20This%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20by%2060%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20model%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20UNICEF%20and%20all%20the%20international%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20is%20evidently%20proud%3B%20the%20model%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%2016%20countries%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20They%20realised%20that%2060%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%20are%20due%20to%20sepsis.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20started%20educating%20village%20health%20workers%20%E2%80%98Aarogya%20Doot%E2%80%99%20(Health%20Messengers)%20to%20detect%20and%20treat%20neonatal%20infections.%20This%20brought%20down%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20to%2020%20per%201%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducate%20adolescents%20about%20s