%20like%20dealing%20with%20regular%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20opines%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Support%20your%20neighbours%20experiencing%20abuse%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20government%20officials%2C%20Prasanna%20believes%20it%20is%20our%20shared%20responsibility%20to%20not%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20when%20these%20incidents%20happen%2C%20neighbours%20feel%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20their%20place%20to%20intervene.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20duty%20to%20offer%20support.%20We%20need%20to%20organise%20programmes%20and%20discussions%20that%20actively%20involve%20community%20members%20in%20decision-making%20and%20foster%20a%20collective%20effort%20to%20tackle%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20assistance%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Prasanna%20through%20the%20Dhwani%20National%20Domestic%20Violence%20Hotline%20at%201800-102-7282%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcvconline.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Prasanna%20Gettu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS%20%E2%80%93%205)%2C%202019%E2%80%9321%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Published%20by%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences%20(IIPS)%20and%20ICF.%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728396571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20third%20ever-married%20women%20in%20India%20experiences%20physical%2C%20sexual%2C%20or%20emotional%20violence%20by%20their%20husbands%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20Despite%20such%20atrocious%20cruelty%2C%20many%20cases%20go%20unreported.%20Prasanna%20Gettu%20suggests%20five%20ways%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20respect%2C%20equality%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20working%20towards%20creating%20a%20society%20where%20violence%20is%20not%20tolerated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369214%2Fprasanna-gettu-helps-domestic-violence-survivors-rebuild-lives-suggests-ways-to-end-crime-abuse-in-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Million%20Farmers%20to%208000%20Schools%3A%20How%203%20Startups%20Are%20Writing%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growth%20Story%20in%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20article%20features%20portfolio%C2%A0companies%20of%20Elevar%20Equity%2C%20which%C2%A0is%20also%20an%20investor%20in%20The%20Better%20India.%20Editorial%20integrity%20and%20transparency%20remain%20our%20priority%2C%20and%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20written%20independently%20to%20provide%20an%20unbiased%20view.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20truly%20comprehend%20the%20vast%20economic%20potential%20brimming%20in%20India%2C%20visit%20its%20rural%20heartlands%20%E2%80%93%20like%20driving%20through%20the%20villages%20of%20Hubbali%20district%20in%20Karnataka.%20As%20you%20negotiate%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20of%20the%20road%2C%20notice%20how%20the%20verdant%20landscape%20is%20punctuated%20with%20shops%2C%20now%20and%20then.%20A%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20barcodes%20displayed%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20new%20addition%2C%20as%20shop%20owner%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday%20mornings%20are%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(general%20store)%20that%20he%20runs.%20But%20Ishwargowda%20seems%20unfazed%20by%20the%20slew%20of%20orders.%20He%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20required%20to%20ace%20mental%20math%20while%20attempting%20to%20calculate%20the%20amount%20of%20change%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20a%20customer.%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%20has%20his%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20the%20rhythmic%20order%20of%20business%20%E2%80%94%20with%20transactions%20happening%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20picture%20of%20a%20new%20age%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BUPI%5D%20makes%20things%20hassle-free%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishwargowda%20points%20out.%20However%2C%20building%20a%20successful%20business%20requires%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20integrating%20tech%20into%20transactions%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20loans%20too.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20where%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20rural%20lending%20startups%20comes%20into%20play.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20an%20opportunity%20knocked%20on%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20door%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20visit%20from%20one%20of%20SarvaGram%E2%80%99s%20staff%2C%20offering%20him%20a%20loan%20that%20would%20essentially%20take%20the%20business%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20by%20helping%20Ishwargowda%20purchase%20more%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECynical%20at%20first%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20a%20chance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20results%20are%20reflected%20in%20his%20earnings%20today.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20income%20from%20the%20shop%20is%20between%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20That%20isn%E2%80%99t%20all.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20loan%20lets%20me%20grow%20my%20business%2C%20keep%20more%20stocks%20in%20my%20shop%2C%20and%20sell%20more%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20one%20of%20the%20only%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshops%20in%20the%20Amargol%20area%2C%20the%20demand%20is%20always%20burgeoning%20and%20the%20loan%20is%20helping%20him%20meet%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20integrating%20UPI%20into%20his%20business%20operations%2C%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20kirana%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBy%20integrating%20UPI%20into%20his%20business%20operations%2C%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20provide%20validation%20to%20former%20banker%20and%20SarvaGram%20co-founder%2C%20Utpal%20Isser.%20He%20explains%20how%20the%20success%20of%20rural%20households%20illustrates%20the%20immense%20potential%20they%20hold.%20The%20inspiration%20to%20start%20a%20business%20that%20focussed%20on%20tipping%20the%20scales%20in%20favour%20of%20such%20homes%2C%20struck%20Utpal%20while%20leading%20the%20rural%20and%20inclusive%20banking%20division%20at%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20sector%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20provided%20him%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20the%20transformation%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20ecosystem%20was%20undergoing%2C%20while%20also%20highlighting%20the%20limitations%20of%20formal%20banking%20institutions%20and%20systems%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20conducive%20to%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWatching%20this%20upward%20mobility%20and%20shift%20in%20infrastructure%20(both%20public%20and%20digital)%20motivated%20us%20to%20look%20for%20a%20business%20model%20that%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20these%20%5Brural%5D%20markets.%20We%20intended%20to%20target%20underbanked%20but%20creditworthy%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20notes.%20Together%20with%20Sameer%20Mishra%2C%20who%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20rural%20finance%2C%20he%20founded%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20changed%20many%20lives%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20with%20access%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BSarvaGram%5D%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20dream%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20continuing%20success%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20rural%20households%20agency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20creditworthiness%20were%20to%20be%20assessed%20solely%20based%20on%20his%20income%20at%20the%20time%2C%20or%20his%20discretionary%20expenses%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20made%20the%20cut.%20A%20lack%20of%20steady%20income%20was%20why%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20for%20a%20formal%20bank%20loan.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20when%20Utpal%20set%20out%20to%20conceive%20SarvaGram%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20build%20it%20with%20a%20growth-oriented%20ethos%20that%20would%20provide%20loans%20to%20those%20with%20variable%20incomes%2C%20but%20aspirational%20mindsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20household-centric%2C%20data-led%2C%20%E2%80%98high-tech%20high-touch%E2%80%99%20distribution%20platform%E2%80%9D%2C%20SarvaGram%20is%20extending%20a%20hand%20towards%20rural%20India%20through%20its%20bouquet%20of%20financial%20and%20productivity-enhancing%20offerings.%20The%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20services%20has%20been%20a%20keen%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunderbanked%20but%20creditworthy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUyhbciwOdQ8%3Fsi%3DJKgdl5rOGHAG-GMb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20this%20into%20perspective%2C%20Utpal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20mid-income%20households%20that%20may%20not%20necessarily%20have%20banking%20records%20or%20credit%20track%20records%20to%20prove%20their%20creditworthiness.%20Instead%2C%20their%20creditworthiness%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20%E2%80%98intent%20to%20repay%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20not%20data-dark%20households%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20ripples%20of%20SarvaGram%20are%20currently%20reaching%20over%2016%2C000%20villages%20across%20India%2C%20making%20it%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20tech%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20scale%20the%20dreams%20of%20households%20that%20once%20did%20not%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20formal%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishwargowda%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20his%20association%20with%20SarvaGr