Priya%20says.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20times%20Priya%20has%20found%20herself%20in%20such%20instances%20has%20made%20her%20indifferent%20today%3B%20she%20has%20her%20life%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20point%20I%20was%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20clarify%20it%20on%20my%20personal%20account%2C%20and%20ask%20everybody%20to%20report%20it.%20And%20most%20times%20it%20gets%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20checked%20after%20it%20four%20days%20later%20and%20the%20profile%20was%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143543%2Ffacebook-ncw-women-internet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Instagram%20have%20the%20option%20to%20make%20a%20profile%20private.%20Nirali%20says%20that%20it%20is%20an%20important%20preventive%20step.%20But%20for%20some%20people%2C%20a%20private%20profile%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20point%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20so%20indifferent%20about%20it%20because%20as%20someone%20with%20a%20public%20account%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20make%20my%20account%20private%3B%C2%A0%20I%20do%20aim%20to%20be%20a%20creator.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20account%20to%20be%20private%20just%20because%20people%20can%20misuse%20my%20information%20if%20I%20have%20a%20public%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20friends%20have%20also%20been%20subject%20to%20becoming%20the%20face%20of%20cyber%20scams.%20Nirali%20explains%20that%20this%20is%20not%20uncommon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20much%20we%20can%20do%20to%20prevent%20it%20because%20of%20the%20freely%20available%20technology.%20See%2C%20I%20believe%20technology%20is%20never%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20purpose%20for%20which%20you%E2%80%99re%20using%20it%20that%20shapes%20it%20up.%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20is%20a%20wonderful%20thing%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20we%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20this%20rise%20of%20AI%20images%20and%20stuff%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20organisation%2C%20we%20get%20complaints%20with%20screenshots%20of%20people%20telling%20young%20girls%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20share%20such%20a%20picture%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20nudify%20your%20image%E2%80%99.%20How%20many%20women%20would%20actually%20go%20and%20complain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20has%20spoken%20to%20some%20of%20her%20fake%20accounts%3B%20not%20the%20ones%20that%20nudified%20her.%20There%20were%20others%20who%20used%20her%20picture%20to%20run%20elaborate%20scams.%20%E2%80%9CLike%2C%20It%20had%20happened%20earlier%20as%20well.%20Somebody%20made%20a%20fake%20account%2C%20with%20a%20bio%20saying%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%E2%80%99%20and%20it%20was%20leading%20them%20to%20a%20spam%20link.%20So%20that%20is%20still%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says%2C%20elucidating%20how%20the%20volume%20of%20such%20crimes%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20any%20confirmative%20action%20to%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20never%20got%20flagged%20down%20by%20the%20platform%20despite%20several%20reports.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20follow%20a%20similar%20pattern.%20Most%20of%20them%20have%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%20in%20this%20link%E2%80%99%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20link.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20spam%2C%20where%20they%20can%20hack%20your%20account%20and%20something%20like%20that.%20All%20these%20accounts%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20of%20myself%20and%20my%20friends%20have%20that%20link%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20has%20even%20engaged%20with%20one%20of%20her%20fake%20profiles.%20One%20that%20had%20the%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%E2%80%99%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20I%E2%8